You never know what someone’s going through, famous or otherwise.

Donna sat down with and new author @madisonbeer to talk about her new book and more, including body dysmorphia and how seeing so many negative comments about her body in youth has impacted Beer to this day.

Offering some advice to young people on social media, Beer said to not judge others and avoid spending too much time on the applications because “life is very short.”
An important conversation surrounding fame and mental health 🖤
